For this repository:
git remote add origin https://github.com/EmrysAlbiorix/EmrysAlbiorix.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
echo "# EmrysAlbiorix" >> README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main

or

General Creation:
git remote add origin https://github.com/"username"/"name".git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
